{"lemma":"خادِمٌ","slug":"خادِمٌ","root":"خ.د.م","root_slug":"خ-د-م","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-د-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10169"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%85%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"domestic servant or (male) manservant (female) maidservant"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"employee"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"attendant"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"waiter (restaurant server)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deacon"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"server"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Active participle of the verb خَدَمَ (ḵadama, “to serve”)."},"ipa":["/xaː.dim/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10169","headword_ar":"خَادِمٌ","root":"xdm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A servant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Mgh, * Msb, * K, * TA;) applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a male:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and, (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAdimapN","text_ar":"خَادِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) each in chaste Arabic, (TA,) but the latter rare, (Msb,) to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young woman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a female:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xad~aAmN","text_ar":"خَدَّامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] is also used in the same sense as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAdimN","text_ar":"خَادِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAdimN","text_ar":"خَادِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xadamN","text_ar":"خَدَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, Mgh, Msb, K,) or rather this is a quasi-pl. n., (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xud~aAmN","text_ar":"خُدَّامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xadamapN","text_ar":"خَدَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and vulgarly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xudomaAnN","text_ar":"خُدْمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) It is said in a trad., of 'Abd-Er-Rahmán, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~aqa A@moraA^atahu famat~aEahaA bixaAdimK sawodaA='a","text_ar":"طَلَّقَ ا@مْرَاَتَهُ فَمَتَّعَهَا بِخَادِمٍ سَوْدَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He divorced his wife, and gave her on that occasion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a black young woman"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as a slave]. (Mgh, * TA.) In the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnapu xaAdimapu gadFA","text_ar":"فُلَانَةُ خَادِمَةُ غَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAdmp","text_ar":"خادمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not properly an epithet: the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a woman will be a servant to-morrow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^iDapN gadFA","text_ar":"حَايِضَةٌ غَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","JK"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}